notes:
Hi Team,

Daniel meet Bobby, Bobby meet Daniel.

Let’s take this time to introduce everyone fully and discuss the lighting plan for our upcoming clinic.

Just so you both are aware, and we have probably mentioned this already, this is BY FAR our client’s most important clinic for their future. This means everything has to PERFECT. They will have some very senior executives scrutinizing our every move. Lighting is going to be one of the most important pieces for us to nail down. No pressure :)

With all that said, we know that with all the experience you guys have, and being bonafide experts, we have no worries that we won’t lose any brownie points from our client because of the lights.

Looking forward to speaking tomorrow!

Best,

Billy
